casebody.data:
RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2009-1935. State v. Fletcher.

Licking App. No. 2009-CA-0055, 2009-Ohio-5650. Reported at 124 Ohio St.3d 1444, 2010-Ohio-188, 920 N.E.2d 374. On motion for reconsideration. Motion denied.

Cupp, J., dissents and would grant the motion as to Proposition of Law No. I and hold the cause for the decision in 2009-2028, State v. Davis, Licking App. No. 09-CA-0019, 2009-Ohio-5175.

Motion for stay of consideration of motion for reconsideration denied.
